The Peoples Democratic Party (PDP), on Saturday, held its presidential campaign in Lokoja, the capital of Kogi. Atiku Abubakar, presidential candidate of the party; Ifeanyi Okowa, vice-presidential candidate; Aminu Tambuwal, Sokoto governor; Udom Emmanuel, governor of Akwa Ibom; and Iyorchia Ayu, PDP national chairperson, were at the rally. See pictures below.           